{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/signalgroupprotocol\/onnotifytarget(flags:handler:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@discardableResult"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyTarget"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ConnectFlags","text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"kind":"text","text":" = ConnectFlags(0), "},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SignalGroupRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject14SignalGroupRefV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/SignalGroupRef"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ParamSpecRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","te